u need to clean the toilet quickly, how easy is this? Now for super tough stains, some light scrubbing might be required, but the product does all the heavy lifting for you. I want this soft life for all of us. In Canada, you can get it at Walmart, Fortino, Shoppers Drug Mart, Superstore, Metro, Sobeys, Freshco, Home Depot, Jean Coutu, and Amazon."}, {"shortCode": "DZ7y-1ARmnI", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZ7y-1ARmnI/", "caption": "I want you to feel this in your bones. Perfection serves no one, it gets us stuck and keeps us from trying, failing, course-correcting and getting ahead. Push through the discomfort of not being \u2018perfect\u2019 at keeping your home clean, and instead DO WHAT YOU CAN today and appreciate the \ud83d\udca9 out of yourself for trying! \n\n\u2705Save this for when you need a pep talk. I gotchu! \u2764\ufe0f\n\n\u2705Follow for more cleaning motovation and ideas #cleanmyspace", "timestamp": "2026-06-23T16:00:12.000Z", "videoDuration": 15.486, "videoPlayCount": 10780, "videoViewCount": 5063, "likesCount": 123, "commentsCount": 3, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/729424334_18597678571058971_5831501242558926953_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFal2U-5oSb99rboft2IC68OpsEod3Ow5n3m4A33cJqCIL18gy87YGR6tjzFPyi4gijNToXKgdUO5_rhgQ3mkit&_nc_ohc=PP7IB5AOGnEQ7kNvwFEJEoN&_nc_gid=x_-op1RwLwLWlrpiilCrWw&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQBXYm52jQSOJ8ire3_C4ZY9TmSk2WxtIDw_-Y9bMjDqXg&oe=6A61D31C&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://instagram.frkh1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQMQt9f3Lhdla1C_mcbmc6y8A6VI11yB65OIhbSfinrwTgoot7ELYWp5mX0ClL5AaidBCY50rnIg5-DOsuEK_UTIuwigPhUDg1iG9Hs.mp4?_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Adp-BxnJQtb4ZWRvvOTg9Yi0moiLtXKdPo0vd7pdtKEHiE-RpDzQOn9kY_Sqx0O212M&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=instagram.frkh1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=esFRwuxQsIEQ7kNvwHbpQmT&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIs